From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Matter Controller Daemon <matter-controller@example.com>
Date: $(date +%Y-%m-%d)
Subject: [PATCH] Add Matter Controller Daemon

Add a new persistent Matter Controller daemon application that:
- Provides persistent Matter Controller functionality
- Supports BLE commissioning (always-on)
- Supports multi-admin commissioning
- Auto-opens commissioning window on startup
- Uses persistent storage at /var/lib/matter-controller/
- Integrates with Thread/OTBR (wpan0)

This is a separate application from chip-all-clusters-app and chip-tool.

